    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "And so on."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Taking C major as an example, '4321' represents a chord progression connected as F (IV chord) => E (iii chord) => D (ii chord) => C (I chord)."
