    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Does it feel uplifting and then suddenly return to calm?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Different note connections create different progression colors and evoke different feelings‚Äîchoose the combinations you like!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Although theoretically you can combine any chords within the key, different chords have different sonic characteristics. For example, the I chord sounds the most stable because the root of the scale is C."
        }
      ]
